cognise that persons with disabilities have the right to the enjoyment of the highest attainable standard of health without discrimination on the basis of disability</span><span style="color:#4c4c4c; font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; font-style:italic">…</span><span style="color:#4c4c4c; font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; font-style:italic">In particular states shall provide persons with disabilities with the same r</span><span style="color:#4c4c4c; font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; font-style:italic">ange, quality and standard of free or affordable health care and programmes as provided to other persons, including in the area of sexual and reproductive health.</span><span style="color:#4c4c4c; font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">’</span></li></ol><p style="line-height:14pt; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 36pt"><span style="color:#4c4c4c; font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><ol start="3" type="1" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt"><li style="color:#4c4c4c; font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 14.17pt; padding-left:3.83pt; text-indent:0pt"><span style="color:#4c4c4c; font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">Over a billion people, about 15% of the world's population, have some form of disability</span><span style="color:#4c4c4c; font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">.</span><a name="_ftnref1"></a><a href="#_ftn1">[1]</a><span style="color:#4c4c4c; font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt"> </span><span style="color:#4c4c4c; font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">R</span><span style="color:#4c4c4c; font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">ates of disability are increasing</span><span style="color:#4c4c4c; font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">,</span><span style="color:#4c4c4c; font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt"> </span><span style="color:#4c4c4c; font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">in part </span><span style="color:#4c4c4c; font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">due to </span><span style="color:#4c4c4c; font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">ageing p</span><span style="color:#4c4c4