:Arial; font-size:11pt"> that are at </span><span style="color:#4c4c4c; font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">ris</span><span style="color:#4c4c4c; font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">k </span><span style="color:#4c4c4c; font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">of</span><span style="color:#4c4c4c; font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt"> falling between</span><span style="color:#4c4c4c; font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt"> programmes </span><span style="color:#4c4c4c; font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">that </span><span style="color:#4c4c4c; font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">focus on</span><span style="color:#4c4c4c; font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt"> health, disability </span><span style="color:#4c4c4c; font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">or</span><span style="color:#4c4c4c; font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt"> women’s rights: </span></li></ul><p style="line-height:14pt; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 54pt; text-indent:-18pt"><span style="color:#4c4c4c; font-family:Symbol; font-size:11pt"></span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; </span><span style="color:#4c4c4c; font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold">Unsafe abortion</span><span style="color:#4c4c4c; font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt"> that each year causes around</span><span style="color:#4c4c4c; font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt"> 5 million women to suffer temporary or permanent disability</span><span style="color:#4c4c4c; font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">,</span><span style="color:#4c4c4c; font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt"> with rates highest amongst poor and rural women. One in four women who undergo an unsafe abortion is likely to develop temporary o</span><span style="color:#4c4c4c; font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">r</span><span style="color:#4c4c4c; font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt"> lifelong disability requiring medical care.</span><a name="_ftnref5"></a><a href="#_ftn5">[5]</a><span style="color:#4c4c4c; font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt"> Women who are dis</spa